{"ja329:0.1":"Jataka ","ja329:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","ja329:0.3":"Kutidusakavagga ","ja329:0.4":"9. Kalabahujataka ","ja329:1.1":"“Yam annapanassa pure labhama, ","ja329:1.2":"Tam dani sakhamigameva gacchati; ","ja329:1.3":"Gacchama dani vanameva radha, ","ja329:1.4":"Asakkata casma dhananjayaya”. ","ja329:2.1":"“Labho alabho yaso ayaso ca, ","ja329:2.2":"Ninda pasamsa ca sukhanca dukkham; ","ja329:2.3":"Ete anicca manujesu dhamma, ","ja329:2.4":"Ma soci kim socasi potthapada”. ","ja329:3.1":"“Addha tuvam panditakosi radha, ","ja329:3.2":"Janasi atthani anagatani; ","ja329:3.3":"Katham nu sakhamigam dakkhisama, ","ja329:3.4":"Niddhavitam rajakulatova jammam”. ","ja329:4.1":"“Caleti kannam bhakutim karoti, ","ja329:4.2":"Muhum muhum bhayayate kumare; ","ja329:4.3":"Sayameva tam kahati kalabahu, ","ja329:4.4":"Yenaraka thassati annapana”ti. ","ja329:5.1":"Kalabahujatakam navamam. "}